# 008 — Charts & visualization (Part H)

## Spec reference

- `C:\GitHub\Berreman\specs\0022\.spec-md` — parent spec (Spec 0022). This slice owns **Part H**.
- `C:\GitHub\Berreman\specs\0022\.slices\001.slice-md` — slice 001 (Part A §A.6) fixed the chart-technology split (ScottPlot + WebView2/Plotly.NET + OpenTK) and the `chartSettings` slot.
